    "description": "<strong>Ashes of the Union</strong> — 一款带有类roguelike元素的车辆射击游戏，为玩家呈现了苏联另类未来的狂野视角。打造您的战车，向大自然展示谁才是老大！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091390/extras/0e92f8eab182ac331a681047367e5f1e.poster.avif?t=1731512207\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091390/extras/0e92f8eab182ac331a681047367e5f1e.webm?t=1731512207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091390/extras/0e92f8eab182ac331a681047367e5f1e.mp4?t=1731512207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>苏联后末日：</strong>沉浸在这样一种氛围中：您舒适的公共公寓已被一个自主掩体所取代。忘记猫和狗吧。在这个世界上，您最喜欢的“宠物”将是巨大的角甲虫和致命的咀嚼蟹。但别担心，它们不会咬人……太疼。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091390/extras/c705e0b44baf5bbb4fd061cf7dc77b96.poster.avif?t=1731512207\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091390/extras/c705e0b44baf5bbb4fd061cf7dc77b96.webm?t=1731512207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091390/extras/c705e0b44baf5bbb4fd061cf7dc77b96.mp4?t=1731512207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>为您的车辆配备各种武器：</strong>苏联风格的改装！将您的旧“Bukhanka”变成配备火箭发射器和激光炮的轮式堡垒。现在您不仅要穿越荒地，还要驯服它们！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091390/extras/9258217f605624a65f38b8ab4ad5bf20.poster.avif?t=1731512207\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091390/extras/9258217f605624a65f38b8ab4ad5bf20.webm?t=1731512207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091390/extras/9258217f605624a65f38b8ab4ad5bf20.mp4?t=1731512207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>探索地图并寻找资源：</strong>穿越废墟的旅程从未如此令人兴奋！穿越废墟，收集稀有资源，避开毒雾，因为我们还没有解毒剂（目前）。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091390/extras/6e4bb5010805e92f7eb768c70f547b75.poster.avif?t=1731512207\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091390/extras/6e4bb5010805e92f7eb768c70f547b75.webm?t=1731512207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091390/extras/6e4bb5010805e92f7eb768c70f547b75.mp4?t=1731512207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>苏联技术模型：</strong>感受苏联工程的力量和可靠性！使用从“GAZ”到“Ural”的各种车辆穿越危险地区并与怪物战斗。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091390/extras/Moдели_советской_техники.gif?t=1731512207\" /></span><br><br><strong>技术发展：</strong>从卡拉什尼科夫坦克机枪到激光炮，从普通木板到最坚固的铸造装甲。升级您的技术，增加您的生存机会，成为荒地之王（或女王）。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091390/extras/74f822a3491626ec61870ec3ee62f0a3.poster.avif?t=1731512207\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091390/extras/74f822a3491626ec61870ec3ee62f0a3.webm?t=1731512207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091390/extras/74f822a3491626ec61870ec3ee62f0a3.mp4?t=1731512207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>您准备好在这个只有智慧和古老的“PKT”才能帮助您生存的世界里展开新的冒险了吗？让我们前进吧，同志们！<br><br>",
